description: Token AIPE, released by the AIPE Foundation headquartered in Singapore, aims to empower cryptocurrency trading through the use of artificial intelligence. It envisions a complete blockchain AI prediction ecosystem, comprised of three core solutions — 3PIKS, an AI-powered price prediction system backed by collective human intelligence through the employment of a user rewards system; AIBitBip, an AI-based price prediction signal push notification service; and AI Auto Trading Bot, an automated trading service taking advantage of the entire AIPE ecosystem.
name: AI Prediction Ecosystem
